description: Chef Jim Ballad of Bargersville was born to serve a noble mission to provide the foodies of Indy with global dishes. Now he has graced us with this traveling truck and it’s sending your taste buds on quite a trip. Whether it’s French, Asian, Mexican, or American, this delicious authentic international street food is downright guaranteed to delight and yes, it’s loads cheaper than an international flight. You’ll savor this sensory teleportation experience when you’re tasting fantastic tacos, sandwiches, and salads of various cultures and cuisines. If you’re suffering from Wanderlust, then a visit to this wonderfully worldly truck is an absolute must.
name: Traveling Taste Buds
